
 Critter - A command line client for Crucible
==============================================

 DEPENDENCIES
==============

Required
    * Qt 4.5 (or newer)
      (c++ library, also used for future gui work)
      http://qt.nokia.com/

    * Boost Program_options
      (Boost c++ library for handling application options)
      http://www.boost.org/

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


 IMPORTANT INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
================================

To compile from source, please refer to the INSTALL file.

